            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I had an opportunity to interview for school Counselor position with the MD.\nBut the MD was so rude during the discussion round. He was not ready to offer a decent scale for my qualifications and experience rather told that counselling is not required for our students we just need to have a Counselor for sake of having, and gave a counter offer of part time with lowest pay scale, despite knowing the strength of the students being 2000 and above. However the principal was understanding. But the MD does not want to pay the staff with respect to their qualifications. Please don’t compromise for any less with his counter offers.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
